## You may have seen my demo, if you are in the SF Bay Area:
### It took me 3 months to figure out how to make a VR game from scratch, using Unity, Blender, and Oculus SDK. Stay tuned to my Twitter for links to an article about how I did it, and updates on the release of the game!
